Chordate's head was spinning.  Feline had kissed him, her purring adding onto 
it nicely, and then she had rubbed his chest, which was very pleasurable.  
She was definately not like any Maximal he had ever met.  Not that he was 
complaining.

With one hand, he gently lifted her head.  "It's ok." he said, kissing her, 
wishing that THIS moment would last forever.
